datasetPresenter.description:

  The <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/popset" target="_blank">NCBI Popset database</a> is a collection of related gene, or partial gene, DNA sequences derived from population, phylogenetic, mutation and ecosystem studies that have been submitted to GenBank. VEuPathDB downloads sequences and associated metadata from the NCBI Popset database that are attributed to taxa represented in PlasmoDB.<br><br>

